                {
                    "id": "5.5",
                    "label": "No global crash",
                    "status": "done",
                    "note": "Pre-flight critical failures raise ExtractionError (not bare exceptions). Per-row failures isolated. Mid-scan DatabaseError caught and returns partial results. Tested by test_mid_scan_corruption_returns_partial."
                },
