                    "id": "5.6",
                    "label": "Structured anomalies output",
                    "status": "done",
                    "note": "ctx.add_anomaly() called for every failure with type/severity/stage/message/context. FailedRow.to_dict() tested. Tested by test_anomaly_emitted_* suite."
